parameters:
\n<\N[3]>What is this place... It's more like a casino than
a game center.
\n<\N[3]>...Anyway, I need to talk to those girls.

\n<???>Finally, you've shown up. So, you still can't give
up on Onee-san, huh?

\n<???>Luna-ne, she's beautiful, you know~. But, isn't
the age difference a bit too much?

\n<???>...You really are a pervert... Ugh... Scary... I'm
going to be attacked...

\n<\N[3]>That's not it. In order to stop the phenomenon of
madness, I need to talk to her once.

\n<???>That's why I'm telling you not to do it. Do you
really think we'll just obey you adults?

\n<\N[3]>If we don't stop it, there will be casualties. Are
you willing to accept that, Ichiru Kurube?

\n<???>...Are you trying to compare me to those bastards
from the organization? I follow my own beliefs and
principles. Don't lump me together with those
villains!

\n<\N[3]>In that case, aren't those guys from the
organization the same? They can come up with all
sorts of justifications and excuses.

\n<???>...Fine. Alright, if you can defeat us, I'll tell
you. Let's have a showdown and see which ideology
prevails.

\n<???>...So you're really going to do it? Ugh... Then
Komari will do her best too...
\n<???>...Hmm, is the usual formation okay, Ichiru?

\n<???>Hey, you two better not slack off as Aria's
underlings!

\n<\N[3]>...Ugh! I have no choice but to take on all three
of them...!

\n<???>...Tch...! You're more persistent than I thought.
Seems like I underestimated you...!
\n<???>...This old man has more skills than I thought...

\n<???>...I told you, if you have something you want to
ask, defeat us first...!

\n<\N[3]>Haa...! Haa...! If that's the case, I can't hold
back anymore...

\c[2]We have detected a certain number of defeats
or more.\c[0] As a relief measure, you can skip to
the situation after winning.\c[0] Will you proceed
with the execution?
コマリが裸で出現（中央）

イチル\SE[default]\n<???>Tch... I can't believe I lost... I let my guard
down. My power has dulled ever since I started
relying too much on your abilities...

イチル\SE[default]\n<???>I already learned my lesson when I was with those
losers...

アイ\SE[default]\n<???>Well, don't worry about it. It's not all Ichiru's
fault, so there's no need to feel down.
アイ\SE[default]\n<???>I also have about 2% of the responsibility.

コマリ\SE[default]\n<???>Aria-chan... I couldn't support you... But, that's
right, Ichiru-chan... It's because Komari's
support was lacking...

イチル\SE[default]\n<???>Taking responsibility is the leader's job! After
all, I'm the one who's been using my head for you
guys!

イチル\SE[default]\n<???>...There's only one way for a yakuza to take
responsibility...! Bring me that thing! I'll take
the responsibility of defeat and cram it in my
ass...!
\n<\N[3]>Wait a minute! I won't allow that!

イチル\SE[default]\n<???>...Ngh...! ...That's right...! Just an encore
won't be enough... I've tarnished Onee-san's
reputation... I'll leave behind not just one, but
both of my legs!
\n<\N[3]>Stop it! Geez, what a dangerous girl...

\n<\N[3]>No, that's not it. Just like our initial
agreement, I just want to ask that girl, Luna,
about something.

イチル\SE[default]\n<???>...!? You're saying you don't need an encore or
legs!?

\n<\N[3]>There's no way you're here... What on earth do you
think I am to you...

イチル\SE[default]\n<???>...Damn it! Onee-san is our benefactor... but,
that's right... a man doesn't break promises.

イチル\SE[default]\n<???>...Fine, I don't know everything about that
person. But I'll still answer if it's something I
know...

\n<\N[3]>Who is she... \c[2]Luna\c[0]? What is her
connection to the phenomenon of madness, the urban
development project in Sakutsuki City?

イチル\SE[default]\n<???>...Onee-san suddenly appeared before us one day.
It was as if she appeared out of nowhere, just
like a mist, and then...

イチル\SE[default]\n<???>...However, I have heard Onee-san's name before in
a conversation between my shitty old man and
someone important involved in that project...
\c[2]Luna\c[0].

イチル\SE[default]\n<???>...She was called like this. \c[2]Hisube
Luna\c[0]. Luna nee-san didn't introduce herself
with her last name in front of us, but it's not a
common name. It's probably her full name.

\n<\N[3]>\c[2]Luna\c[0]...! Her name was also mentioned in
that document... a huge corporation... but if I
remember correctly, the Hikou Group withdrew from
urban development projects...

イチル\SE[default]\n<???>I don't know the details about that. I have
nothing to do with that shitty old man's business.
But, it's true that the shitty old man was
involved in something shady, there's no doubt
about that...

イチル\SE[default]\n<???>I don't know how much she was involved in it...
but ever since I met her, the city has been
overflowing with madmen... It's hard to believe
that it's unrelated to the phenomenon.

アイ\SE[default]\n<???>...There was one time when I asked Luna nee-san
about something. How did you do that?

アイ\SE[default]\n<???>Just touching the desires that everyone holds...
Well, she's always been someone hard to grasp and
says things that are hard to understand, so I just
let it slide.

\n<\N[3]>Just by touching...? But if that's the case,
there's no doubt that she is the cause...

イチル\SE[default]\n<???>...Wait a minute!! There's no way that person... a
young girl alone could do something like that! The
backs of those guys are against her, I'm sure of
it...

\n<\N[3]>It seems like there's a misunderstanding, but I
don't want to arrest her specifically. I just want
to stop the phenomenon.

\n<\N[3]>If she can help resolve and counteract the
phenomenon, I want her to cooperate. That's really
all there is to it. And I understand that it's not
something a young girl can do alone.

\n<\N[3]>However, if the damage worsens from here on... it
will surpass the level that I can handle. It will
undoubtedly be a backlash that a young girl alone
cannot possibly contend with.
コマリ\SE[default]\n<???>...Luna-san is probably at the next station.

コマリ\SE[default]\n<???>If it's this old man, I won't do anything bad...
I'm different from Ichiru-chan's father, Ai-chan,
and Komari's parents...

コマリ\SE[default]\n<???>I don't even think about Komari and the others...
They're just tools, possessions... I don't even
consider them human. I'm surely different from
those who think that way. Yes... That's what I
believe.

コマリ\SE[default]\n<???>For Komari, Luna-san is not just someone she owes
her life to, but also a benefactor. That's why she
wants you to stop Luna-san... Uncle, she wants you
to...

\n<\N[3]>...That girl is... she's at the next station,
right?

\n<\N[3]>...Understood, it's a promise. I will stop her and
make sure nothing bad happens. I will help her.
